[3] USA (California, Butte county)
Date: Thu 18 Apr 2019 4:20 PM PDT
Source: Action News Now [abridged, edited]
https://www.actionnewsnow.com/content/news/Now-7-confirmed-measles-cases-in-Butte-County-508778101.html


Butte County Public Health officials have confirmed one additional case of measles in an adult from Butte county.

Measles public exposure location in Chico and Oroville have been identified for this case. Public health officials stress that the investigation into this case is ongoing and more locations are expected to be added.

Butte County Public Health has confirmed one additional case of measles in an adult, bringing the total of cases in the county to 7. These cases are linked to the original measles cluster announced on 24 Mar 2019.

This is a developing story ...

